# PartyKit — real-time sync via Yjs
#
# Local dev:  run `npx partykit dev` in a second terminal → host is localhost:1999
# Production: run `npx partykit deploy` → host is comic-forge.<you>.partykit.dev
#
# Without this set, the editor runs in local-only mode (no sync, fully functional).
NEXT_PUBLIC_PARTYKIT_HOST=localhost:1999
